Tinplate
Drawability, as well as world class gauge control, shape and surface, make the tin mill products of USS-POSCO second to none.  One third of USS-POSCO product line is tinplate which we produce for the canning industry. Drawability, as well as world class gauge control, shape and surface, make the tin mill products of USS-POSCO second to none. Can manufacturers will realize productivity increases because of our consistently high quality. We supply material for welded body and end applications as well as, drawn and iron can, coil fed operations and draw redraw.  Continuous cast, continuous annealing, double reduction and other advanced processes keep USS-POSCO Industriesâ tinplate a step ahead of the competition. Our exceptional formability enables high speed can lines to produce greater quantities more efficiently. USS-POSCO Industriesâ superior delivery performance, reduced lead time programs, and manufacturing flexibility shortens your supply chain allowing for reduced inventory investment. Our goal is to make doing business with USS-POSCO Industries easy and to be a contributor to improving your companyâs bottom line.  Please contact us. 



 
